        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"normalp3\">长洲沈处士三白以〈浮生六记〉见示，分赋六绝句</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n    </div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"calibre5\">刘樊仙侣世原稀，瞥眼风花又各飞； 赢得红闺传好句，“秋深人瘦菊花肥”。（君配工诗，此集中遗句也）</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"calibre5\">烟霞花月费平章，转觉闲来事事忙； 不以红尘易清福，未妨泉石竟膏肓。</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"calibre5\">坎坷中年百不宜，无多骨肉更离披； 伤心替下穷途泪，想见空江夜雪时。</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"calibre5\">秦楚江山逐望开，探奇还上粤王台； 游踪第一应相忆，舟泊胥江月夜杯。</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"calibre5\">瀛海曾乘汉使槎。中山风土纪皇华； 春云偶住留痕室，夜半涛声听煮茶。</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n\t</div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"calibre5\">白雪黄芽说有无，指归性命未全虚； 养生从此留真诀，休向嫏環问素书。</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000068": {
