        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><h2 class=\"calibre3\">题词二</h2></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n  </div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"calibre5\">是编合冒巢民《影梅盦忆语》、方密之《物理小识》、李笠翁《一家言》、徐霞客《游记》诸书，参错贯通，如五侯鲭，如群芳谱，而绪不芜杂，指极幽馨。绮怀可以不删，感遇乌能自已，洵《离骚》之外篇，《云仙》之续记也。向来小说家标新领异，移步换形，后之作者几于无可著笔，得此又树一帜。惜乎卷帙不全，读者犹有遗憾；然其凄艳秀灵，怡神荡魄，感人固已深矣。</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n  </div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"calibre5\">仆本恨人，字为秋士。对安仁之长簟，尘掩茵帱；依公瑕之故居，种寻药草（余居定光寺西，为前明周公瑕药草山房故址）。海天琐尾，尝酸味于芦中；山水邀头，骋豪情于花外。我之所历，间亦如君；君之所言，大都先我。惟是养生意懒，学道心违，亦自觉阙如者，又谁为补之欤？浮生若梦，印作珠摩（余藏旧犀角圆印一，镌“浮生若梦”二语）；记事之初，生同癸未（三白先生生于乾隆癸未，余生于道光癸未）。上下六十年，有乡先辈为我身作印证，抑又奇已。聊赋十章，岂惟三叹。</p></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n  </div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><div class=\"quote1\"> 艳福清才两意谐，宾香阁上斗诗牌。\n    深宵同啜桃花粥，刚识双鲜酱味佳。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    琴边笑倚鬓双青，跌宕风流总性灵。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    商略山家栽种法，移春槛是活花屏。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    分付名花次第开，胆瓶拳石伴金罍。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    笑他琐碎板桥记，但约张魁清早来。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    曾经沧海难为水，除却巫山不是云。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    守此情天与终古，人间鸳牒只须焚。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    衅起家庭剧可怜，幕巢飞燕影凄然。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    呼灯黑夜开门去，玉树枝头泣杜鹃。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    梨花憔悴月无聊，梦逐三春尽此宵。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    重过玉钩斜畔路，不堪消瘦沈郎腰。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    雪暗荒江夜渡危，天涯莽莽欲何之？<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    写来满幅征人苦，犹未生逢兵乱时。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    铁花岩畔春多丽，铜井山边雪亦香。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    从此拓开诗境界，湖山大好似吾乡。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    眼底烟霞付笔端，忽耽冷趣忽浓欢。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    画船灯火层寮月，都作登州海市观。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    便做神仙亦等闲，金丹苦炼几生悭。<br class=\"calibre1\">\n    海山闻说风能引，也在虚无缥缈间。</div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\">\n  </div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/492fad9ebad71b30/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-0feac4 twpub-492fad9ebad71b30-9882b5\"><div class=\"calibre1\"><p class=\"right\"> 同治甲戌初冬，香禅精舍近僧题。    </p></div></div>"
        },
